荃錦公路原是[[駐港英軍|駐港英軍]]的軍用道路，在1950年，駐港英軍為方便運送軍用車輛和物資出入新界及進行防禦工事，請來同在[[肯亞|肯亞]]和[[馬來半島|馬來半島]]修築道路的[[皇家工兵部隊|英國皇家工程隊]]來港發展[[軍事|軍事]][[建築工程|建築工程]]，建造一條往返[[荃灣|荃灣]]和[[錦田|錦田]]的山麓公路<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-hk|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqokITq0d46uX3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20all_dc.title%3A%28%22%E8%8F%AF%E5%83%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%22%29%29%20AND+%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_freetext_filter=1950-10-21&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_log=Y|title=荃灣闢路至錦田 全路十五咪 分十段開投|publisher=華僑日報|date=1950-10-21|page=5|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904013656/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqokITq0d46uX3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28+all_dc.title%3A%28%22%E8%8F%AF%E5%83%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%22%29%29+AND+%28+verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C+HK%5C+Newspapers%22%29%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_freetext_filter=1950-10-21&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_log=Y|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當時指揮工程者，為加溫第[[准將|准將]]（{{lang|en|Brigadier H. P. Cavendish}}）<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-hk|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2Bh5KT9sfcXnNHHcHrKDEY8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=11&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281951-10-02%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281951-10-02%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281951-10-02%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281951-10-02%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281951-10-02%